{"type": "article", "id": 17780, "title": "指向手势的长椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-19T06:30:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000356tVMb09TC4NdFZlxc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tMudra 在梵文里代表一种礼貌的手势，这种手势在印度文化包括瑜伽艺术中都非常重要，象征着一种均衡和入定。印度设计师 Karan Singh Gandhi 以这种手势为原型，做了这把桦木椅，左右对称，形成柔和的曲面。椅子的两侧微微上扬，四周都有柔和的弧度，令人感到舒服。座位下面用了很细的白色金属杆，模拟了两手交叉的感觉，在此对比下座位像是漂浮在空气中。<a href=\"http://karansinghgandhi.com\" target=\"_blank\">这里是设计师的主页。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060003546ZOgq09bxAPNnlGH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.38571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060003542NPhkavgy3oSC7D4.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000355xpzySbs2lj0BOq4J.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000355MVvPTz2HmqEYRrLZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}